quran[14{c,v,t}:
21,11,kitni hi zalim bastiyan hain jin ko hum ne pees kar rakh diya aur unn ke baad doosri kisi qoum ko uthaya
21,12,jab unn ko hamara azaab mahsoos howa to lagey wahan se bhagnay
21,13,"( kaha gaya )"" bhago nahi, jao apne unhi gharon mein aur aish ke samanon mein jin ke andar tum chain kar rahay thay, shayad ke tum se poocha jaye """
21,14,"kehnay lagey"" haae hamari kam bakhti, be shak hum khata waar thay """
21,15,"aur woh yahi pukarte rahay yahan taq ke hum ne un ko khalyaan kar diya, zindagi ka aik sharara taq un mein nah raha"
21,16,hum ne iss aasman aur zameen ko aur jo kuch bhi un mein hai kuch khail ke tor par nahi banaya hai
21,17,agar hum koi khilona banana chahtay aur bas yahi kuch hamein karna hota to apne hi paas se kar letay
21,18,magar hum to baatil par haq ki chout lagatay hain jo is ka sir toar deti hai aur woh dekhte dekhte mِt jata hai aur tumahray liye tabahi hai unn baton ki wajah se jo tum banatay ho
21,19,zameen aur aasman mein jo makhlooq bhi hai Allah ki hai aur jo ( farishtay ) is ke paas hain woh nah apne aap ko bara samajh kar uss ki bandagi se sartabi karte hain aur nah malool hotay hain
21,20,"shab o roz is ki tasbeeh karte rehtay hain, Dam nahi letay"
21,21,kya inn logon ke banaye hue arzi khuda aisay hain ke ( be jaan ko jaan bakhash kar ) uttha khara karte hon ?
21,22,agar aasman o zameen mein aik Allah ke siwa doosray khuda bhi hotay to ( zameen aur aasman ) dono ka nizaam baggar jata pas pak hai Allah Rab ul Arsh unn baton se jo yeh log bana rahay hain
21,23,woh apne kamon ke liye ( kisi ke agay ) jawab da nahi hai aur sab jawab da hain
21,24,"kya ussay chore kar unhon ne dosray khuda bana liye hain? ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho ke"" lao apni Daleel , yeh kitaab bhi mojood hai jis mein mere doori ke logon ke liye nasiyaat hai aur woh kitaaben bhi mojood hain jin mein mujh se pehlay logon ke liye nasiyaat thi"" magar un mein se aksar log haqeeqat se be khabar hain, is liye mun moray hue hain"
